<section class="cta-final">
  <div class="cta-wrap reveal">

    <h2>Ton coach IA t'attend.<br/><em>Il connaît déjà ta stratégie.</em></h2>

    <p class="cta-sub">
      Crée ton profil en 5 minutes, importe tes trades,
      et reçois ton premier débrief dès dimanche soir.
    </p>

    <div class="cta-proof-row">
      <div class="cta-proof">⚡ Setup en 5 min</div>
      <div class="cta-proof">📅 Debrief dès dimanche</div>
      <div class="cta-proof">🇫🇷 Données en France</div>
      <div class="cta-proof">💬 Support Discord direct</div>
    </div>

    <a href="https://app.mytradingcoach.app/register" class="cta-btn">
      Commencer gratuitement →
    </a>
    <p class="cta-note">Gratuit sans CB · Premium : essai 7 jours, aucun prélèvement avant · Annulable à tout moment</p>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-final {
    padding: 100px 5%;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cta-final::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 100%, rgba(59,130,246,.08), transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .cta-wrap { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; }
  .cta-final h2 {
    font-family: var(--disp); font-size: clamp(28px,5vw,44px);
    font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -.5px; color: var(--txt);
    line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .cta-final h2 em { color: var(--blue2); font-style: normal; }
  .cta-sub { font-size: 16px; color: var(--txt2); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 32px; font-weight: 300; max-width: 460px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

  .cta-proof-row {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .cta-proof {
    font-size: 12px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--txt2);
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--b);
    padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 100px;
  }

  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--blue); color: white;
    text-decoration: none; padding: 16px 40px;
    border-radius: 12px; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700;
    font-family: var(--disp);
    box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(59,130,246,.4);
    transition: background .2s, box-shadow .2s, transform .2s; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .cta-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(59,130,246,.5); }
  .cta-note { font-size: 12px; color: var(--txt3); font-family: var(--mono); }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .cta-final { padding: 60px 16px 80px; }
    .cta-proof-row { gap: 8px; }
    .cta-proof { font-size: 11px; padding: 5px 10px; }
    .cta-btn { font-size: 15px; padding: 14px 28px; }
  }
</style>
